\n附件：臺灣臺北地方檢察署檢察官聲請簡易判決處刑書111年度\r\n      調院偵字第385號。","JFULLPDF":"https://data.judicial.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/TPDM/111%2c%e5%8e%9f%e4%ba%a4%e7%b0%a1%2c36%2c20220926%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"TPDM,111,原交簡,36,20220926,1","JYEAR":"111","JCASE":"原交簡","JNO":"36","JDATE":"20220926","JTITLE":"過失傷害"}